    "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you." : {
      "comment" : "Description for SilencePodPreference.enabled",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Všechna upozornění Pod nepoužívají žádné zvukové signály a zvukové signály potvrzující připomenutí jsou potlačeny. Pod vydává zvukové signály pouze v případě fatálních poruch Pod a při přehrávání testovacích signálů.\n\n⚠️Warning - Pokud se váš telefon nachází mimo dosah pod, zatímco je tato funkce zapnutá, nebudete dostávat žádná upozornění v aplikaci; a pod vás nebude upozorňovat zvukovým signálem."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Toutes les alertes du Pod n'utilisent aucun bip et les bips de rappel de confirmation sont désactivés. Le Pod émettra un bip uniquement en cas de défaut fatal du Pod et lors des bips de test.\n\n⚠️Avertissement - Si votre téléphone est hors de portée du Pod pendant que cette fonctionnalité est activée, vous ne recevrez aucune notification dans l'application ; et le Pod ne bipera pas pour vous alerter."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tutti gli avvisi del Pod non emettono alcun segnale acustico e i segnali acustici di promemoria di conferma vengono soppressi. Il Pod emetterà un segnale acustico solo in caso di guasti irreversibili del Pod e durante la riproduzione di segnali acustici di prova. \n \n⚠️Avviso: se il telefono è fuori dalla portata del Pod mentre questa funzione è attivata, non riceverai alcuna notifica in-app e il Pod non emetterà alcun segnale acustico di avviso."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "すべてのポッド・アラートはビープ音を使用せず、確認のリマインダー・ビープ音は抑制されます。Podがビープ音を鳴らすのは、致命的なPod故障のときと、テストビープ音を再生するときだけです。\n\n⚠️Warning - この機能が有効になっている間、携帯電話がポッドの圏外にある場合は、アプリ内通知を受け取らず、ポッドがビープ音を鳴らして警告することもありません。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "모든 파드 알림은 비프음을 사용하지 않으며 확인 알림 비프음은 억제된다. 파드는 치명적인 파드 결함이 있을 때와 테스트 비프음을 재생할 때만 비프음을 울린다.\n\n⚠️Warning - 이 기능이 활성화되어 있는 동안 휴대폰이 파드의 범위를 벗어나면 인앱 알림을 받지 못하며, 파드에서 경고음을 울리지 않습니다."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Alle pod-varsler bruker ingen pipelyder, og bekreftelsespipelyder undertrykkes. Pod piper bare ved fatale pod-feil og når testpipelyder spilles av. \n \n⚠️Advarsel – Hvis telefonen din er utenfor rekkevidde for pod mens denne funksjonen er aktivert, vil du ikke motta noen varsler i appen, og pod vil ikke pipe for å varsle deg."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Alle Pod alarmen gebruiken geen biepen en bevestigingspunten worden onderdrukt. De Pod zal alleen piepen bij fatale Pod gebreken en bij het spelen van testpiepen.\n\n⚠️Waarschuwing - Als je telefoon buiten bereik is als deze functie is ingeschakeld, krijg je geen in-app meldingen; en de pod zal niet piepen om je te waarschuwen"
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Toate alertele pompei sunt fără semnale sonore, iar notificările de confirmare sunt suprimate. Pompa va emite semnale sonore doar în cazul erorilor grave de pompă și atunci când se redau semnale sonore de test. \n \n ⚠️Atenție - Dacă telefonul dumneavoastră este în afara razei de acțiune a pompei în timp ce această funcție este activată, nu veți primi nicio notificare în aplicație; iar pompa nu va emite semnale sonore pentru a vă alerta."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "sk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "sl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vsa opozorila Pod ne uporabljajo zvočnih signalov, zvočni signali opomnika za potrditev pa so utišani. Pod se oglasi le ob usodnih napakah pod in ob predvajanju testnih signalov.\n\n⚠️Warning - Če je vaš telefon zunaj dosega pod, ko je ta funkcija omogočena, ne boste prejeli nobenih obvestil v aplikaciji, pod pa vas ne bo opozoril s piskom."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Alla Pod varningar använder inga pip och bekräftelse påminnelsen pip undertrycks. Pod kommer endast att pipa för dödliga Pod fel och när du spelar testpip.\n\n⚠️Varning - Om din telefon är utom räckhåll för poden medan denna funktion är aktiverad, kommer du inte att få några meddelanden i appen; och poden kommer inte att pipa för att varna dig."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tất cả cảnh báo của Pod không phát tiếng bíp, và tiếng bíp nhắc xác nhận cũng bị tắt. Pod chỉ phát tiếng bíp khi xảy ra lỗi nghiêm trọng hoặc khi thực hiện bài kiểm tra tiếng bíp.\n\n⚠️ Cảnh báo – Nếu điện thoại của bạn ngoài phạm vi kết nối với Pod khi tính năng này được bật, bạn sẽ không nhận được bất kỳ thông báo nào trong ứng dụng, và Pod cũng sẽ không bíp để cảnh báo bạn."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "All Pod alerts use no beeps and confirmation reminder beeps are suppressed. The Pod will only beep for fatal Pod faults and when playing test beeps.\n\n⚠️Warning - If your phone is out of range of the pod while this feature is enabled, you will not receive any in-app notifications; and the pod will not beep to alert you."
          }
        }
      }
    },
