            "value" : "Si prega di portare solo il Pod originale nel raggio d'azione o disattivare il Pod originale"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "範囲内にオリジナルポッドのみを持ち込むか、オリジナルポッドを無効化してください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "범위 내에 오리지널 포드만 가져오거나 오리지널 포드를 비활성화하세요."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ta kun med original pod innenfor rekkevidde eller deaktiver original pod"
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Breng alleen de oude pod binnen bereik of deactiveer de originele pod"
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Używaj tylko oryginalny POD w zasięgu sygnału albo dezaktywuj oryginalny POD"
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please bring only original pod in range or deactivate original pod"
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vă rugăm să aduceți doar pompa inițială în rază de acțiune sau dezactivați pompa inițială"
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Пожалуйста, приносите в зону действия только оригинальный под или деактивируйте оригинальный под"
          }
        },
        "sk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Prosím, majte iba pôvodný pod v dosahu alebo deaktivujte pôvodný pod"
          }
        },
        "sl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "V območje prinesite samo originalni pod ali deaktivirajte originalni pod."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ha endast din ursprungliga podd inom räckvidd eller inaktivera ursprunglig podd"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lütfen menzile yalnızca orijinal podu getirin veya orijinal podu devre dışı bırakın"
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Будь ласка, тримайте лише вихідний Pod у зоні дії або деактивуйте оригінальний Pod"
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Chỉ mang pod gốc trong phạm vi hoạt động hoặc hủy kích hoạt pod gốc"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please bring only original pod in range or deactivate original pod"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached." : {
      "comment" : "Alert message body for confirm pod attachment",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Zkontrolujte, zda je pod bezpečně připevněn k tělu.\n\nKanylu lze do každého přístroje Pod zavést pouze jednou. Když je Pod připojen, klepněte na \"Confirm\" (Potvrdit)."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bekræft venligst, at Pod er sikkert fastgjort til din krop.\n\nKanylen kan kun indsættes én gang med hver Pod. Tryk på \"Bekræft\", når Pod er tilsluttet."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bitte vergewissere Dich, dass der Pod sicher an Deinem Körper befestigt ist.\n\nDie Kanüle kann mit jedem Pod nur einmal eingeführt werden. Tippe auf „Bestätigen“, wenn der Pod angeschlossen ist."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Compruebe que el Pod está bien adherido a su cuerpo.\n\nLa cánula sólo puede insertarse una vez con cada Pod. Pulse \"Confirmar\" cuando el Pod esté ya bien adherido a su cuerpo."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Veuillez confirmer que le Pod est solidement attaché à votre corps. \n\n La canule ne peut être insérée qu'une seule fois avec chaque Pod. Appuyez sur \"Confirmer\" lorsque le Pod est appliqué."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Si prega di confermare che il Pod è saldamente fissato al corpo.\n\nLa cannula può essere inserita una sola volta con ogni Pod. Tocca \"Conferma\" quando il Pod è fissato."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ポッドが身体にしっかりと固定されていることを確認してください。\n\nカニューレは1つのPodにつき1回しか挿入できません。Podが装着されたら「確認」をタップしてください。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pod가 본체에 단단히 부착되어 있는지 확인하세요.\n\n캐뉼라는 각 Pod마다 한 번만 삽입할 수 있습니다. Pod가 부착되면 \"확인\"을 탭합니다."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vennligst bekreft at pod er godt festet til kroppen din.\n\nKanylen kan bare settes inn én gang med hver pod. Trykk på \"Bekreft\" når pod er festet til kroppen."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Controleer of de Pod goed op je lichaam vastgeplakt zit.\n\nDe canule kan slechts één keer per Pod worden ingebracht. Tik op \"Bevestigen\" wanneer de Pod is vastgeplakt."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Potwierdź, że POD jest poprawnie przymocowany do ciała. \n\nKaniulę można wprowadzić tylko raz w każdym POD'dzie. Stuknij „Potwierdź”, gdy POD jest przymocowany."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vă rugăm să confirmați că pompa este bine fixată de corpul dumneavoastră. \n\nCanula poate fi introdusă doar o singură dată cu fiecare pompă. Atingeți „Confirmați” când pompa este fixată."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Убедитесь, что под надежно приклеен на вашем теле.\n\nКатетер можно ввести только один раз. Нажмите кнопку \"Подтвердить\", когда под приклеен."
          }
        },
        "sk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "sl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Prepričajte se, da je pod varno pritrjen na telo.\n\nKaniulo lahko vstavite samo enkrat z vsakim podom. Ko je Pod pritrjen, tapnite \"Potrdi\"."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kontrollera att podden sitter bra på din kropp.\n\nKanylen kan bara föras in en gång. Tryck på \"Bekräfta\" när podden sitter fast."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lütfen Pod'un vücudunuza güvenli bir şekilde takıldığından emin olun. \n\n Kanül, her Pod ile yalnızca bir kez yerleştirilebilir. Pod eklendiğinde \"Onayla\"ya dokunun."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Vui lòng xác nhận rằng Pod đã được gắn chắc chắn vào cơ thể bạn.\n\nKim tiêm chỉ có thể được chèn một lần cho mỗi Pod. Nhấn “Xác nhận” khi Pod đã được gắn."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please confirm that the Pod is securely attached to your body.\n\nThe cannula can be inserted only once with each Pod. Tap “Confirm” when Pod is attached."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Please deactivate the pod. When deactivation is complete, you may pair a new pod." : {
      "comment" : "Instructions for deactivate pod when pod not on body",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "يرجى إلغاء تفعيل البود. عند اكتمال إلغاء التفعيل، يمكنك إقران بود جديد."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Deaktivujte modul. Po dokončení deaktivace můžete spárovat nový pod."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Deaktiver Poden. Når deaktiveringen er fuldført, kan du parre en ny Pod."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Bitte deaktiviere den Pod. Wenn die Deaktivierung abgeschlossen ist, kannst Du einen neuen Pod koppeln."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
