    "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes." : {
      "comment" : "Alert content body for suspendEnded pod alert",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Období pozastavení podávání inzulínu skončilo.\n\nPodávání můžete obnovit z banneru na domovské obrazovce nebo z obrazovky nastavení pumpy. Za 15 minut vám bude znovu připomenuta."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Perioden for suspension af insulin er afsluttet.\n\nDu kan genoptage afgivelsen fra den øverste del af startskærmen eller fra skærmen med pumpeindstillinger. Du vil blive mindet om dette igen om 15 minutter."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Insulinabschaltung ist beendet.\n\nDu kannst die Abgabe über das Banner auf dem Startbildschirm oder über den Bildschirm mit den Pumpeneinstellungen fortsetzen. Du wirst in 15 Minuten erneut erinnert."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "El periodo de suspensión de la insulina ha finalizado.\n\nPuedes reanudar la administración desde el banner de la pantalla de inicio o desde la pantalla de ajustes de tu bomba. Se le recordará de nuevo en 15 minutos."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "La période de suspension de l'insuline est terminée. \n\nVous pouvez relancer l'administration à partir de la bannière sur l'écran d'accueil ou à partir de l'écran des paramètres de votre pompe. Vous recevrez un nouveau rappel dans 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il periodo di sospensione dell'insulina è terminato. \n \nPuoi riprendere l'erogazione dal banner nella schermata iniziale o dalla schermata delle impostazioni della pompa. Riceverai un altro promemoria tra 15 minuti."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "インスリンの中断期間は終了した。\n\nホーム画面のバナー、またはポンプ設定画面から投与を再開できます。15分後に再度リマインダーが表示されます。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "인슐린 일시 중단 기간이 종료되었습니다.\n\n홈 화면의 배너 또는 펌프 설정 화면에서 배송을 재개할 수 있습니다. 15분 후에 다시 알림이 표시됩니다."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Perioden med insulinsuspensjon er avsluttet.\n\nDu kan gjenoppta leveringen fra banneret på startskjermen eller fra skjermbildet for pumpeinnstillinger. Du vil bli påminnet igjen om 15 minutter."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De insulineonderbrekingsperiode is verstreken.\n\nJe kunt de toediening hervatten op het startscherm of via je pompinstellingenscherm. Over 15 minuten wordt je er opnieuw aan herinnerd."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Okres zawieszenia podawania insuliny dobiegł końca. \n\nPodawanie można wznowić za pomocą banera na ekranie głównym lub na ekranie ustawień pompy. Ponowne przypomnienie pojawi się za 15 minut."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Perioada de suspendarea a administrării de insulină s-a încheiat.\n\nPuteți relua administrarea din bannerul de pe ecranul principal sau de pe ecranul de setări al pompei. Vi se va aminti din nou în 15 minute."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Период приостановки подачи инсулина закончилось.\n\nВы можете возобновить введение инсулина с баннера на главном экране приложения или с экрана настроек вашей помпы. Через 15 минут вы получите повторное напоминание."
          }
        },
        "sk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Obdobie pozastavenia inzulínu sa skončilo.\n\nPodávanie inzulínu môžete obnoviť z bannera na domovskej obrazovke alebo z obrazovky nastavení pumpy. Pripomienka sa vám znova zobrazí o 15 minút."
          }
        },
        "sl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Obdobje začasne ukinitve inzulina se je končalo.\n\nDostavljanje lahko obnovite s transparenta na začetnem zaslonu ali z zaslona z nastavitvami črpalke. Ponovno boste opomnjeni čez 15 minut."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Planerad period av paus av pump är slut.\n\nDu kan återuppta insulintillförsel i pumpinställningar. Du kommer bli påmind igen om 15 minuter."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "İnsülin askıya alma süresi sona ermiştir.\n\nAna ekran üzerinden veya pompa ayarları ekranınızdan iletime devam edebilirsiniz. 15 dakika içinde tekrar hatırlatılacaktır."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Thời gian tạm dừng tiêm insulin đã kết thúc.\n\nBạn có thể tiếp tục tiêm từ thanh thông báo trên màn hình chính hoặc từ cài đặt bơm. Bạn sẽ nhận nhắc nhở lần nữa sau 15 phút."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The insulin suspension period has ended.\n\nYou can resume delivery from the banner on the home screen or from your pump settings screen. You will be reminded again in 15 minutes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced." : {
      "comment" : "Description text for critical alerts",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Výše uvedená připomenutí nebudou na zařízení znít, pokud je v tichém režimu nebo v režimu Nerušit. Existují další kritická upozornění Pod, která se na vašem zařízení ozvou, i když je nastaveno v režimu Tichý nebo Nerušit.\n\nZařízení Pod bude také používat zvukové signály pro všechna připomenutí a upozornění zařízení Pod s výjimkou případů, kdy je zařízení Pod v režimu Tichý."
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "fi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Les rappels ci-dessus ne retentiront pas sur votre appareil lorsqu'il est en mode Silencieux ou Ne pas déranger. D'autres alertes Pod critiques retentiront sur votre appareil même lorsqu'il est réglé sur Silencieux ou Ne pas déranger.\n\nLe Pod émettra également des bips sonores pour tous les rappels et alertes Pod, sauf lorsque le Pod est en mode silencieux."
          }
        },
        "he" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "hu" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "I promemoria sopra indicati non emetteranno suoni sul tuo dispositivo quando questo è in modalità Silenziosa o Non Disturbare. Ci sono altri avvisi critici del Pod che emetteranno suoni sul tuo dispositivo anche quando è impostato su Silenziosa o Non Disturbare.\n\nIl Pod emetterà inoltre segnali acustici per tutti i promemoria e gli avvisi del Pod, tranne quando il Pod è silenziato."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "上記のリマインダーは、デバイスがサイレントモードまたはDo Not Disturbモードの場合は鳴りません。サイレントモードまたは「迷惑をかけない」モードに設定されていても、デバイスに音が鳴る重要なPodアラートが他にもあります。\n\nPodは、Podがサイレンスになっているとき以外は、すべてのPodリマインダーとアラートに可聴ビープ音を使用します。"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "기기가 무음 또는 방해 금지 모드에 있을 때는 위의 알림이 기기에서 울리지 않습니다. 무음 또는 방해 금지 모드로 설정되어 있어도 장치에서 울리는 다른 중요한 Pod 알림이 있습니다.\n\n또한, 파드가 무음 상태인 경우를 제외하고 모든 파드 리마인더와 경고에 대해 경고음이 울린다."
          }
        },
        "nb" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Påminnelsene ovenfor vil ikke høres hvis enheten er i Stille- eller Ikke forstyrr-modus. \nDet er andre kritiske pod-varsler og alarmer som vil høres selv om enheten er satt til Stille eller Ikke forstyrr-modus.\n\nPod vil også bruke lydsignaler for alle pod-påminnelser og -varsler, bortsett fra når pod er i Lydløs-modus."
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Als je apparaat stil is of in de Niet storen-modus staat, hoor je de bovenstaande herinneringen niet in de app. Er zijn echter andere belangrijke waarschuwingen voor de Pod die nog steeds in de app verschijnen, zelfs als je apparaat stil is of in de Niet storen-modus staat.\n\nDe Pod maakt ook geluid met piepjes voor alle herinneringen en waarschuwingen, behalve als de Pod is uitgeschakeld."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "ro" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Avertismentele de mai sus nu vor suna pe dispozitivul dumneavoastră atunci când acesta este în modul Silențios sau Nu deranjați. Există și alte alerte critice ale pompei care vor suna pe dispozitivul dumneavoastră chiar și atunci când este setat în modul Silențios sau Nu deranjați. \n\nPompa va utiliza, de asemenea, semnale sonore pentru toate notificările și alertele de pompă, cu excepția cazului în care pompa este în mod silențios."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "sk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "sl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Zgornji opomniki se v napravi ne bodo oglasili, če je naprava v načinu Tiho ali Ne moti. Obstajajo tudi druga opozorila Pod, ki se v napravi oglasijo, tudi če je nastavljena na način Tiho ali Ne moti.\n\nPod bo uporabljal tudi zvočne signale za vse opomnike in opozorila Pod, razen kadar je Pod utišan."
          }
        },
        "sv" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Påminnelser kommer vara tysta när du har tyst läge eller stör ej - läge på. \n\nDet finns andra varningar som kommer att ljuda även vid tyst läge eller stör ej - läge, förutom om podden är tystad."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Các nhắc nhở trên sẽ không phát tiếng trên thiết bị của bạn khi ở chế độ Im lặng hoặc Không làm phiền. Tuy nhiên, còn có các cảnh báo Pod quan trọng sẽ vẫn phát tiếng ngay cả khi thiết bị ở chế độ Im lặng hoặc Không làm phiền.\n\nPod cũng sẽ phát tiếng bíp cho tất cả các nhắc nhở và cảnh báo, trừ khi Pod đang ở chế độ im lặng."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The reminders above will not sound on your device when it is in Silent or Do Not Disturb mode. There are other critical Pod alerts that will sound on your device even when set to Silent or Do Not Disturb mode.\n\nThe Pod will also use audible beeps for all Pod reminders and alerts except when the Pod is Silenced."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The time on your pump is different from the current time. Do you want to update the time on your pump to the current time?" : {
      "comment" : "Message for pod sync time action sheet",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "الوقت في مضختك مختلف عن الوقت الحالي. هل ترغب في تحديث الوقت في مضختك ليتوافق مع الوقت الحالي؟"
          }
        },
        "cs" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Čas na čerpadle se liší od aktuálního času. Chcete aktualizovat čas na čerpadle na aktuální čas?"
          }
        },
        "da" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tiden på din pumpe er forskellig fra den aktuelle tid. Vil du opdatere tiden på din pumpe til det aktuelle tidspunkt?"
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die Uhrzeit Deiner Pumpe unterscheidet sich von Deiner aktuellen Uhrzeit. Möchtest Du die Uhrzeit Deiner Pumpe auf Deine aktuelle Uhrzeit aktualisieren?"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The time on your pump is different from the current time. Do you want to update the time on your pump to the current time?"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
